title: Intel True Fabric Scale Switches: Slot Temperature Sensors
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/intel
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the temperature sensors of the slots of
 of True Scale Fabric Switches which support the ICS-CHASSIS MIB.

 For each sensor connected to a slot the status can be invalid (CRIT),
 unknown (UNKNOWN), bad (CRIT), warning (WARN), good (OK) or
 disabled (UNKNOWN).

 Moreover the temperature reading is reported.

item:
 The slot ID.

inventory:
 One service is created for each slot.
